product_name: Keen Bryce WP Hiking Shoes - Women's
long_description: Made to help you move fast and light on the trail, the women's Keen Bryce Waterproof Hiking Shoes provide waterproof protection and sturdy support while tackling your favorite day hike. Waterproof nubuck leather and flexible nylon mesh uppers are flexible and breathable; low coverage saves weight on trails when you need minimal support. KEEN.DRY(TM) waterproof, breathable membranes keep feet dry while allowing perspiration to dissipate before it saturates the inside of the shoe. Patented rubber Toe Guards protect feet and uppers from impacts and abrasion. Removable, dual-density EVA footbeds combine with KEEN.ZORB strobel boards for excellent shock absorption and step-in comfort. Compression-molded, dual-density EVA midsoles offer shock absorption and padding for all-day comfort. Supportive thermoplastic urethane shanks enhance torsional stability on uneven terrain. The women's Keen Bryce Waterproof Hiking Shoes feature nonmarking rubber outsoles that deliver all-around traction.
